            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "It would seem so. We want to fix it, but we don't have the materials... I don't know what to do."
